###  https://w3id.org/pmd/tto/TTO_0000030
<https://w3id.org/pmd/tto/TTO_0000030> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       rdfs:subClassOf co:PMD_0050154 ;
                                       rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://w3id.org/pmd/tto> ;
